t\":\"分镜视频\",\"agent_workflow_tooltip_no_storyboard\":\"无分镜图生成\",\"agent_workflow_tooltip_not_available\":\"图片暂未生成\",\"agent_workflow_video_synthesis\":\"视频合成\",\"agree_to_statement\":\"支付即视您已同意\",\"agreement_checkbox_text\":\"开通前请阅读%s\",\"ai_content_tip\":\"内容由 AI 生成\",\"ai_tools_page_desc\":\"发现更多 AI 图像与视频工具，轻松开启创作新玩法 🔥\",\"ai_tools_page_title\":\"AI魔法工具\",\"all\":\"所有\",\"all_reference\":\"全能参考\",\"all_section_text\":\"集全\",\"all_submissions_section\":\"所有作品\",\"announcement_button_seedance2_try_it_now\":\"体验新版创作页\",\"announcement_button_try_it_now\":\"立享优惠\",\"announcement_heading\":\"全能图片Pro会员免费用！\",\"announcement_heading_seedance2\":\"焕新升级第一步：全新创作体验\",\"announcement_seedance2_body_0\":\"项目空间上线：每个创作，专属空间\",\"announcement_seedance2_body_1\":\"更强模型，更好工具 — 焕新升级，正在开始\",\"announcement_seedance2_title_0\":\"多模态统一创作，图片、视频、音频，一处完成\",\"announcement_seedance2_title_1\":\"资产管理升级：整理、查找、随取随用\",\"announcement_text_1\":\"12月31号前，所有会员无限使用🍌全能图片Pro模型生图！\",\"announcement_text_2\":\"V3.1（媲美Veo3.1）与S2.0（媲美Sora2.0）上线，享受更强大的内容创作能力！\",\"announcement_title_1\":\"Hailuo 2.3 \u0026 2.3 Fast 重磅发布！\",\"announcement_veo_body\":\"解锁高达 63% 的折扣，通过订阅专属的高级生成质量、更快的性能和独家功能，提升您的创作流程。不要错过这个难得的机会 — 立即升级！\",\"announcement_veo_body_title_0\":\"以无与伦比的价格体验Veo 3.1的全部功能。\",\"announcement_veo_title\":\"限时63%优惠购买Veo系列！\",\"annual_biggest_discount_banner\":\"海螺年度最大折扣来袭，全年仅此一次，开通会员享受更多专属权益\",\"annual_master_unlimited_deadline\":\"大师年会员：5月1日前海螺视频无限生成\",\"annual_ultra_unlimited_deadline\":\"至臻年会员：6月1日前海螺视频无限生成\",\"api_btn\":\"获取API\",\"app_IG_SR_Image_btn\":\"图片\",\"app_ai_edit_detail_source_tag\":\"原始\",\"app_bonus_credtis_notif_popup\":\"🎁 本月充值福利还未领取，月底前充值享额外积分！\",\"app_bounts_credits\":\"赠送\",\"app_camera_enable_models_toast\":\"在{{model}}模型下使用\",\"app_camera_permission\":\"需要相机权限以拍摄照片和视频，创作精彩内容\",\"app_describe_ai_edit_title\":\"智能改图\",\"app_detail_tool_page_image_subtitile_1\":\"核心工具\",\"app_detail_tool_page_image_subtitile_2\":\"增强\",\"app_detail_tool_page_image_subtitile_3\":\"美容与肖像\",\"app_detail_tool_page_title\":\"工具游乐场\",\"app_detail_tool_page_video_subtitile_1\":\"核心工具\",\"app_detail_tool_page_video_subtitile_2\":\"营销工具\",\"app_detail_tool_page_video_subtitile_3\":\"AI技巧\",\"app_disabled_frame_params_toast\":\"{{disableFrameParams}}视频不支持使用尾帧\",\"app_download_desc\":\"专业的AI视频生成工具，支持文生视频、图生视频，采用新一代AI模型，让视频创作更快捷。快速生成高品质视频内容，带来极致的创作体验。支持自定义镜头语言、运镜路径和角色形象，打造电影级画质效果。从创意到成片，让AI视频创作更精准、更专业。\",\"app_download_title\":\"海螺视频App - 在手机上便捷的表达创意\",\"app_free_start_end_frame_text\":\"9月10日 16:00～17日 16:00，使用首尾帧功能生成视频，将不扣除账户积分！快去试试吧～！\",\"app_free_start_end_frame_title\":\"🎁 首尾帧7天限时免费！\",\"app_h5_IG_AC_assets\":\"我的资产\",\"app_h5_IG_AC_copy_link\":\"复制分享链接\",\"app_h5_IG_AC_new_creation\":\"重新创作\",\"app_h5_IG_AC_s2i\":\"参考主体生图\",\"app_h5_IG_AC_s2v\":\"参考主体生视频\",\"app_h5_IG_AC_video_it\":\"生成视频\",\"app_h5_IG_SR_change\":\"更换图片\",\"app_h5_IG_SR_confirm\":\"确认\",\"app_h5_IG_SR_no_face\":\"未检测到人脸\",\"app_h5_IG_SR_no_face_window_btn\":\"更换图片\",\"app_h5_IG_SR_no_face_window_subtitle\":\"请上传一张至少有一个清晰人脸的图片\",\"app_h5_IG_SR_no_face_window_title\":\"未检测到人脸\",\"app_h5_IG_SR_recognizing\":\"识别中\",\"app_h5_IG_add_cr\":\"添加参考角色（选填）\",\"app_h5_IG_add_cr_selected\":\"参考角色\",\"app_h5_IG_photo_album\":\"相册\",\"app_h5_IG_photo_camera\":\"拍照\",\"app_h5_IG_photo_history\":\"从最近的上传中选择\",\"app_h5_IG_photo_select\":\"选择\",\"app_h5_IG_propmt_optimization\":\"自动优化\",\"app_h5_IG_setting_model\":\"模型\",\"app_h5_IG_setting_ratio\":\"图片尺寸\",\"app_h5_create_page_a2i_title_1\":\"图片生成\",\"app_h5_create_page_a2i_title_2\":\"将灵感转化为生动的图像\",\"app_h5_create_page_creation_select\":\"请选择创建方式\",\"app_h5_create_page_i2v_title_1\":\"图生视频\",\"app_h5_create_page_i2v_title_2\":\"让你的图片动起来\",\"app_h5_create_page_image_generation_subtitle\":\"让创意变得生动可见\",\"app_h5_create_page_s2v_title_1\":\"主体参考\",\"app_h5_create_page_s2v_title_2\":\"使用固定角色创建视频\",\"app_h5_create_page_t2v_title_1\":\"文生视频\",\"app_h5_create_page_t2v_title_2\":\"将你的创意变成视频\",\"app_h5_create_page_upload\":\"点击上传图片\",\"app_hero_section_1\":\"生成图片\",\"app_hero_section