得3000奖励积分！\",\"special_offer_subscribe_buy_credits_title\":\"购买即送！\",\"special_offer_subscribe_card_hover_info\":\"实际获得{total_credits} （{plan_credits}+{bonus_credits}）积分，有效期1个月\",\"special_offer_subscribe_card_title\":\"{bonus_credits} 积分\",\"special_offer_subscribe_tag1_20260115\":\"365 Unlimited\",\"special_offer_subscribe_tag1_20260115_cn\":\"365天无限生成\",\"special_offer_subscribe_tag2_20260115\":\"Nano Banana Pro\",\"special_offer_subscribe_tag2_20260115_cn\":\"全能图片Pro\",\"special_offer_subscribe_title_20260115\":\"获取 365 天无限 Nano Banana Pro x 计划 56% 折扣\",\"special_offer_subscribe_title_20260115_cn\":\"365天全能图片Pro无限生成 x 年会员4.5折！\",\"special_offer_text_365dayunlimited_20260115_cn\":\"365天无限生成\",\"special_offer_text_365unlimited_20260115\":\"365 Unlimited\",\"special_offer_text_getdealnow_20260115\":\"查看优惠\",\"special_offer_text_upgradenow_20260115\":\"立即升级\",\"speed_mode_description\":\"闲时模式将在资源可用时处理您的请求，需要排队等待，「高级会员」用户在此模式下不消耗积分。\\\\n\\\\n 快速模式将立即处理您的请求，无需排队等待。\",\"stage_left\":\"左聚焦\",\"stage_right\":\"右聚焦\",\"star_chat_popup\":\"收藏\",\"star_end_frame_tips\":\"首尾帧\",\"starred_list\":\"收藏夹\",\"start_frame_upload_btn\":\"首帧\",\"start_new_button\":\"重新创作\",\"static_shot\":\"固定镜头\",\"status_invoice_issuance_failed\":\"开票失败\",\"status_processing\":\"处理中\",\"status_refunded\":\"已重开\",\"status_reissue_failed\":\"重开失败\",\"status_reissuing\":\"重开中\",\"status_review_failed\":\"审核失败\",\"status_sent\":\"已发送\",\"status_under_review\":\"审核中\",\"sticky_promo_text\":\"立省s%\",\"storage_permission_toast\":\"保存失败，请开启存储权限\",\"storyboard_add_shot_message\":\"在分镜%s后新增分镜\",\"storyboard_add_shot_tooltip\":\"添加分镜\",\"storyboard_characters\":\"主演造型\",\"storyboard_delete_shot_input_value\":\"删除分镜\",\"storyboard_detail_shot_tab_text\":\"详细分镜\",\"storyboard_final_video\":\"合成视频\",\"storyboard_frame_number\":\"分镜列表\",\"storyboard_generate_shot_img\":\"重新生成分镜%s的分镜图\",\"storyboard_generate_shot_input_value\":\"重新生成\",\"storyboard_loading_scene\":\"生成场景图\",\"storyboard_main_character\":\"主角\",\"